      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――三日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――3 days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "鈴村さん、今日から現場に復帰だけど……\n調子はどう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzumura-san‚ you're returning to the set today‚ but…\nHow are you feeling?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "おかげ様でいつも通りです\nリハはどうでした？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to everyone‚ I'm feeling normal.\nHow was the rehearsal?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "全く問題なかったよ。完全復活だな\nただ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were no issues at all. You're fully recovered.\nHowever…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3044311755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ただ……なんです？　気になることでもありました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However… what? Is there something bothering you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "天動さんと奥山さんの視線が冷たい気がするんだけど\n……鈴村さん、二人に何か言った？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel like Tendo-san and Okuyama-san are giving me cold looks.\n…Did you say something to them‚ Suzumura-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6387668269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、うちがあることないこと吹き込んだって\n疑ってるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you suspecting that I've been spreading rumors?\nThat's mean~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "嫌やわ～\nうちがそんな酷いことするはずないやんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I would never do something like that.\nYou don't think I'm capable of such cruel things‚ do you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.5702956822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yeah‚ you're right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ただ……{user}さんは\nうちの初めての人になりはった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But…I only told them that {user}-san‚\nis my first time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6333433334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "って言うただけです。……いろんな意味で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…In various ways.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "言ってるじゃないか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then you said everything‚ aren't you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、でも嘘はついてへんしなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ well‚ I can't lie.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "初めて部屋に入れて\n初めて看病してもらった男の人なんやし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were the first person to enter my room.\nThe first person to take care of me‚ a man.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "その部分を意図的に隠して伝えてるだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You intentionally left out that part when you told them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、ちゃんとフォローはしときますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ don't worry. I'll cover for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは……\nとっても優しくしてくれはった。って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like‚ {user}-san…\nhave been so soft and kind to me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "勘弁してくれ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Spare me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん達にはちゃんと本当のこと\n言うとくから、安心して下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll tell Rui-chan and Sumire-chan the truth‚\nso don't worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "そのうちな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It'll all work out eventually.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "今すぐにお願いしたいんだけどな……俺の明日のために",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to ask you right away… for the sake of my tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、冗談やんか\n{user}さんはホンマに真面目やなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ just joking.\n{user}-san‚ you're really serious‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、そんな人やから\nうちも安心して看病してもらったんやけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that's just who you are.\nI feel relieved knowing I had someone like you taking care of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "数日とはいえ、心配するファンの声は大きかったよ\n今日のステージで、元気な姿をファンに見せてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though it was only for a few days‚ fans were really worried.\nShow them your energetic self on stage today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、任せて下さい\n休んだ分、今まで以上のうちを見せますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ leave it to me.\nI'll show them an even better side of me to make up for the rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ俺はそろそろ行くよ。よろしく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I'll be going now. Take care.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、{user}さん\nあの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}-san.\nUm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "えーとですね？\n……その",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you see?\n….hmm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、まだどこか具合が悪いのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why? You feel sick again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "違います、そうやなくて……\n…………ん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nah‚ it's not that…\n…Um!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "今回は、ホンマにお世話になりました\nありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really appreciate everything this time.\nThank you very much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "言いにくそうにしてるからなんだと思えば……\nどうしたんだ？　改まって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seemed hesitant to say it…\nWhat's the matter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "うち、照れ隠しでついふざけてまうから……\n本当は、ちゃんとお礼言いたかったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I‚ um‚ I tend to joke around to hide my embarrassment…\nBut the truth is‚ I really wanted to properly thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu021.m4a",
      "text": "このご恩は、これからの仕事でお返ししますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll repay this favor with my work from now on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "今日、これから最高のステージを見せてくれ\n恩返しなら、それが一番だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Show me the best stage today.\nThat's the best way to repay me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu022.m4a",
      "text": "……はい！　任せて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes! Leave it to me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu023.m4a",
      "text": "こんばんはー！　TRINITYAiLEの\n鈴村優です！　今日は、うちらのライブにようこそ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good evening! I'm Yu Suzumura\nfrom TRINITYAiLE! Welcome to our live performance today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 466.6666666999788,
          "startTime": 174.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu024.m4a",
      "text": "先日はうち、風邪でイベント休んで\n心配掛けてしまってごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I apologize for causing you worry\nwhen I had to cancel the event due to a cold the other day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu025.m4a",
      "text": "でも、完全復活です！\nむしろ休養になって、以前より元気なくらいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I'm fully recovered now!\nIn fact‚ the rest actually made me even more energetic than before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu026.m4a",
      "text": "うちな、今回周囲の人に……ファンのみなさんや\nスタッフさんにいっぱい心配してもらって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I realized that everyone‚\nincluding the fans and staff‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu027.m4a",
      "text": "助けてもらってるんやなって、みんなのおかげで\nステージに立ててるんやなって実感しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "were so concerned and supportive of me.\nI'm truly grateful to all of you for allowing me to stand on this stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.7409199289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu028.m4a",
      "text": "うちは幸せ者です\n今夜は目一杯楽しんでいって下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel lucky.\nPlease enjoy tonight to the fullest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu029.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、一曲目いきましょか～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ shall we start with the first song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2466.666666700007,
          "startTime": 220.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "（……いいステージだ。ありがとう、鈴村さん）\n（最高の恩返しだよ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…It's a great stage. Thank you‚ Suzumura-san.）\n（It's the best way to repay.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu030.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu031.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみなさん！　スタッフのみなさん！\nそれから――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To all the fans! To all the staff!\nAnd also…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu032.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと支えてくれる――あなたに\nうちらの歌で恩返し！　最後まで観て下さいねー！",
      "translations": {
